task.summary: Incorporated Tom Hart's Morsecode Choux Choux theme
Fixed bug whereby query parameters wouldn't get carried over upon page change Modified welcome screen Something else which i frankly don't remember
Commented out init values for right HighCharts gadget which caused Javascript errors
Implemented viewable/not viewable switch in Resources page (Nerija) (issue #90) Changed 'Edit' to 'Map' (issue #91) Improved the checkboxes at the top of the Resources page (#93)
Use Redis cache in parts of permisions checking (Sentry is chatty) Update Sentry to 2.1
Swapped the getUnviewable to getViewable Made a series of appearance improvements
Added headings to the various grids

This commit includes an apparently working filter based query generator.
NB: Debug var_dumps are still on, NOR have I checked the numbers returned from ES!

Filters working properly in cumulative way.
* It means that sets of filters added in an AND array. * Fixed the problem of broken queries when subfilter was empty. * When checking for a custom ES mapping being false, check for both FALSE and 'missing'=>('field'=>'fieldname') * Cast 'yes' to true and 'no' to false
Finally, removed debug var_dumps (see previous commits)

A number of fixes included. Also, a lot of eye candy (currency and other icons)
What's missing now for tonight is: 1. Validation 2. The weird good to go workflow thing (same as viewable but where do we put the button?)
First version ohe the Quick view embedded in the main view page
